,"uid":3270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T23:37:26.000Z","msg":"叫人唔好無線玩 咁不如玩返3DS <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b37b053fb30fab4aa626cd4c86af7963c27a4f2","tid":143583,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T00:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一水必出事"},{"pid":"863f1de5ae4f130fe8d57dd1794008cf44906c2f","tid":143583,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T00:21:54.000Z","msg":"索尼：我真係恭喜你呀"},{"pid":"5e4c325323385207fd1fd77c91de9bda66706f94","tid":143583,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T00:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08cb3b2645ed6e6fac671aa309e23aea45a0da6e","tid":143583,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T02:07:36.000Z","msg":"Switch發售首日屏幕問題頻出 藍屏閃屏變磚暫無對策<br />\n<br />\n2017/03/04 22:41<br />\n　任天堂Switch已經於昨日正式發售，不少玩家已經拿到主機。然而，除了之前就已經曝光的手柄連接問題外，似乎還有更多的硬件問題不斷湧現。<br />\n   不少拿到Switch的玩家在社交媒體上放出了自己的主機情況，有很多人反饋機器會出現藍屏、死機的問題，並且聯繫客服售後得到的回答是只能重換系統。目前大家還沒有搞清楚引發這一問題的原因。Reddit上玩家們猜測可能是需要進行首日更新，或者是機器本身的缺陷，但目前還沒有確定的說法。<br />\n   還有的玩家碰到了「橙屏」的情況，也是死機無法操作。不過這種現象可能比較稀少，而且玩家發現按住電源鍵重啓機器可以解決這個問題。<br />\n   　也有玩家反饋了閃屏的問題，這一問題也無法通過重啓解決，他找售後調換了新機。<br />\n　國外一家媒體Glixel則反饋，大概用了一周左右，日常使用時將Switch插入拔出Dock底座會划傷屏幕。準確的說是屏幕左下方的部分，但看起來也不太舒服。Glixel研究後認為是底座設計的問題，玩家如果插入時對不太准的話，就會划傷屏幕。<br />\n        Polygon則試用了任天堂官方出的屏幕保護套，但其設計似乎比整體屏幕要短一些。<br />\n　　至於之前就已經頻繁談到的手柄連接問題，任天堂在官網頁面上給出的對策是切斷機器重連，並排除周圍可能對主機電波有干擾的設備。<br />\n　　另外，國外不少玩家是通過亞馬遜訂購Switch的，但是亞馬遜的物流配送似乎出了一些問題，很多玩家並沒有在第一時間收到預定的主機。推特上也有不少吐槽，有些玩家的配送被推遲到了週末甚至下周，有些還在準備寄送狀態。"},{"pid":"27b0657d25ef1f054274f00ad1dc11a41481f37d","tid":143583,"uid":62691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T02:09:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>繼續等<br />\n等到有二手game先買<br />\n預訂果班今次開心羅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用炒價買o個班 on9先最開心"},{"pid":"25f0dea89e44c2ddef4d63ef85ed66e2e01effea","tid":143583,"uid":55231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T02:11:35.000Z","msg":"咪一樣有一大班人為左隻GAME而買機<br />\n你有你壞 我有我賣"},{"pid":"36bd17aef7a9dbc4fbe86de1ebe024c270330ad1","tid":143583,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T02:17:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://file1.a9vg.com/data/attachment/forum/201703/04/224033zx4oxctc2gszcsno.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffile1.a9vg.com%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201703%2F04%2F224033zx4oxctc2gszcsno.jpg&h=d03349e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23853931b323eb820a483544ecf1b4f470567e4f","tid":143583,"uid":22675,"like