:70505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T05:27:31.000Z","msg":"肯定硬件問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00086df85cc6371c3e8859435369dd1a2b9f988","tid":143583,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T05:45:32.000Z","msg":"之前一早知出事，班人仲仆街仆到去食炒價，出現問題都抵喇<br />\n同埋老任玩飢餓銷售，但係部機太垃圾<br />\n今次中伏果班永無下次買老任產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4abfe420cfc311941da126e38ecd7f0ee67d6bf0","tid":143583,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T05:47:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>預左第1批貨問題多多</blockquote><br />\n無ps4咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一批有彈碟問題，又會變磚頭機</blockquote><br />\nps4彈碟果個問題好易解決到<br />\nswitch一定唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c379e66d851e82e9f6042ffe050305e1bfb5e24","tid":143583,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T05:48:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我記得連登好多任狗<br />\n之前有POST笑柒任記<br />\n個個衝哂出黎護主<br />\n<br />\n去哂邊?</blockquote><br />\n喺晒遊戲台"},{"pid":"8e72c44d7b18493bfcf940f95607625e6729508d","tid":143583,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T05:52:22.000Z","msg":"其他主機好似ps4. Xb有事<br />\n用家會屌間公司<br />\nFf15有bug都俾人屌到上天花板<br />\n<br />\n真係得任地獄既fans會好似隻狗咁護短<br />\n<br />\n主機橙mon，jc接觸不良，吉歪左仲好易整花部機<br />\nZelda又一大堆bug無人理"},{"pid":"a52be3b3f76fc110f3a6cc21c8ef70bb59abfe97","tid":143583,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T03:28:34.000Z","msg":"目前nintendo switch的災情如下<br />\n<br />\n1 遊戲執行中畫面異常(雪花、雜點、顏色反轉、閃爍)：顯卡問題<br />\n<br />\n2 螢幕出現條狀異常、壞亮點：LCD問題<br />\n<br />\n3 持續不止的雜音：音訊晶片或speaker問題<br />\n<br />\n4 當機(黃藍屏)、按鍵或觸控無反應、畫面凍結：系統穩定性<br />\n<br />\n5 手把延遲或斷訊：藍芽晶片功率問題<br />\n<br />\n6 卡夾插入沒反應：卡夾良率<br />\n<br />\n7 接上dock時螢幕刮傷：機構設計不良<br />\n<br />\n8 手把握套無法拆裝、卡死：零件公差過大<br />\n<br />\n9 掌機模式時手把與主機無法緊密結合，會搖：零件公差過大<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60001&amp;snA=40243&amp;tnum=4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D60001%26snA%3D40243%26tnum%3D4&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=5a4a5160\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60001&amp;snA=40243&amp;tnum=4</a>"},{"pid":"ac7f061f79f6b9ad6a953c74ca281c5e4f3e1c0d","tid":143583,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T03:42:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其他主機好似ps4. Xb有事<br />\n用家會屌間公司<br />\nFf15有bug都俾人屌到上天花板<br />\n<br />\n真係得任地獄既fans<span style=\"color: red;\">會好似隻狗咁護短</span><br />\n<br />\n主機橙mon，jc接觸不良，吉歪左仲好易整花部機<br />\nZelda又一大堆bug無人理</blockquote><br />\n咁算唔算抽埋ifansboy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee2587bde7f864747d10a6202371e8cb22416ec","tid":143583,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:17:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/Cb-srOfRqNc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCb-srOfRqNc&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=3c45d4db\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Cb-srOfRqNc</a></blockquote><br />\n片都有啦，仲有假？"},{"pid":"1c08171a745727ce6d84912fb4823b03741c8997","tid":143583,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:38:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}